# Pipeline OUTPUT zone. Every artifact the pipeline produces lands here under a
# standard sub-layout:
#   outbox/index/      vector index        (index --output; search/tui --index)
#   outbox/md/         converted markdown  (convert --output)
#   outbox/chunks/     exported chunks     (export --output)
#   outbox/reports/    JSON run reports    (convert/lint --report)
#   outbox/vocab/      entity vocabulary   (scan --vocab)
#   outbox/taxonomy/   taxonomy + fields   (scan-taxonomy)
#   outbox/dump/       diagnostic dumps    (python -m sdd_pipeline.dump)
# Everything under outbox/ is git-ignored; only this skeleton is tracked.
